author: Watsonite
title: Carl sleeps with the fishes
review:
I buy a lot of these magazine gifts. They are somewhat overpriced but sometimes come with nice figures. These aren't the sets to review but for this one, an exception needed to be made.

I think Carl's trip with his underwater scuba-jet-thingy is most likely his last.
There is simply no way of putting Carl on the handle without the blades chopping him up.

Rebuild the world indeed, but I guess not the way Carl expected it.
